TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ISNULL(in_WM_DEPT_ID) OR ( NOT ISNULL(in_WM_DEPT_ID) AND ( IIF (ISNULL(CREATE_DATE_TIME),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),CREATE_DATE_TIME) != IIF (ISNULL(in_WM_CREATE_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),in_WM_CREATE_TSTMP) OR IIF (ISNULL(MOD_DATE_TIME),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),MOD_DATE_TIME) != IIF (ISNULL(in_WM_MOD_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),in_WM_MOD_TSTMP) OR IIF (ISNULL(CREATED_DTTM),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),CREATED_DTTM) != IIF (ISNULL(in_WM_CREATED_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),in_WM_CREATED_TSTMP) OR IIF (ISNULL(LAST_UPDATED_DTTM),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),LAST_UPDATED_DTTM) != IIF (ISNULL(in_WM_LAST_UPDATED_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),in_WM_LAST_UPDATED_TSTMP) ) )

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ISNULL(i_USER_NAME1) OR ( NOT ISNULL(i_USER_NAME1) AND ( IIF (ISNULL(CREATED_DTTM),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),CREATED_DTTM) != IIF (ISNULL(i_WM_CREATED_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),i_WM_CREATED_TSTMP) OR IIF (ISNULL(LAST_UPDATED_DTTM),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),LAST_UPDATED_DTTM) != IIF (ISNULL(i_WM_LAST_UPDATED_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),i_WM_LAST_UPDATED_TSTMP) ) )

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ISNULL(in_WM_PERF_SMRY_TRAN_ID) OR ( NOT ISNULL(in_WM_PERF_SMRY_TRAN_ID) AND ( IIF (ISNULL(CREATE_DATE_TIME),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),CREATE_DATE_TIME) != IIF (ISNULL(in_WM_CREATE_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),in_WM_CREATE_TSTMP) OR IIF (ISNULL(MOD_DATE_TIME),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),MOD_DATE_TIME) != IIF (ISNULL(in_WM_MOD_TSTMP),TO_DATE('01/01/1900','MM/DD/YYYY'),in_WM_MOD_TSTMP) ) )

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
$$Initial_Load (trunc(E_CONSOL_PERF_SMRY.CREATE_DATE_TIME) >= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')) - 1 ) OR (trunc(E_CONSOL_PERF_SMRY.MOD_DATE_TIME) >= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')) - 1) AND
1=1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
$$Initial_Load (trunc(UCL_USER.CREATED_DTTM)>= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')) - 1) OR (trunc(UCL_USER.LAST_UPDATED_DTTM)>= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')) - 1) AND
1=1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
$$Initial_Load (trunc(CREATE_DATE_TIME) >= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS'))-1) OR (trunc(MOD_DATE_TIME) >= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS'))-1) OR (trunc(CREATED_DTTM) >= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS'))-1) OR (trunc(LAST_UPDATED_DTTM) >= trunc(to_date('$$Prev_Run_Dt','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS'))-1) AND
1=1
